# The single "Maxi80 App" target supports appletvos, but `assemble` builds the
# iOS slice (sdk: iphoneos) and the fastlane base xcconfig
# (Darwin/Maxi80.xcconfig) currently restricts SUPPORTED_PLATFORMS to
# iphoneos/iphonesimulator/macosx. Before adding a tvOS TestFlight/App Store
# binary lane, parametrize `assemble` with an `sdk: "appletvos"` build and
